<h1 class="h2 pt-3 pb-2 mb-3 border-bottom">Wi-Fi</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col col-md-8 col-lg-6">

    <h3 class="mb-3 hstack gap-3">Hotspot mode <div class="vr"></div> <small class="text-muted">broadcast a wireless network</small></h3>
    <p>Let the Raspberry Pi broadcast it's own wireless network.<br>
    The Raspberry Pi's ip address shall be <code>192.168.128.1</code>.</p>

    <div class="row mb-3">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="form-check form-switch">
          <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="toggleWiFi" onclick="toggleWiFi()">
          <label class="form-check-label" for="toggleWiFi">Enable hotspot mode</label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-3">
      <div class="col-3 text-end">
        <label for="staticNetworkName" class="col-form-label">Network Name</label>
      </div>
      <div class="col-9">
        <input input type="text" readonly class="form-control" id="staticNetworkName" value="{{hostname}}">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-3">
      <div class="col-3 text-end">
        <label for="staticPassword" class="col-form-label">Password</label>
      </div>
      <div class="col-9">
        <input input type="text" readonly class="form-control" id="staticPassword" value="{{hostname}}">
      </div>
    </div>

    <p><b>Note:</b> this network shall not have internet access!</p>

    <hr class="my-5">

    <h3 class="mb-3 hstack gap-3">Client mode <div class="vr"></div> <small class="text-muted">join a wireless network</small></h3>
  <form class="needs-validation" novalidate>

    <div class="row mb-3">
      <p>Connect to a known wireless network.<br>
      Enter the <code>ssid</code> and <code>psk</code> to add the network to the Raspberry Pi's <code>wpa_supplicant</code> list.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-3">
      <div class="col-3 text-end">
        <label for="inputNetworkName" class="col-form-label">Network Name</label>
      </div>
      <div class="col-9">
        <input type="text" id="inputNetworkName" class="form-control" spellcheck="false" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" required>
      </div>
    </div>

